zhDesc: 虽然大家是来等夜晚看中秋圆月的，但中秋的落日也吸引了很多目光和相机。

enTitle: Weed with Sunset in the Background

看书忘记了时间，匆忙地向福海西北方赶的路上，回头看到初生的圆月。
赶到“平湖秋月”时，月已升高到天上。

zhDesc: 很意外的机会，我参加了在成都的中国R语言会议。虽然演讲的主题并不是我专长的领域，能够接触到业界和学术界的前沿人物还是很开心的。
enDesc: With a very surprising opportunity, I spoke at the China R Meeting, Chengdu. Even though I presented a topic which is not my specialty, I’m glad to know the frontier of the industrial and academic people.

enDesc: A few fishermen collect their crabbing cages by the bank.

enDesc: Two egrets walk around the river bank.

enDesc: There are a few venders lending North Korean costumes. A little girl has her photo taken in costumes.

zhDesc: 鸭绿江为中朝共有，所以两方的船都可以自由行驶。一些中国游船会靠近朝鲜岸边。
enDesc: Yalu River is shared by China and North Korea, so boats of both sides can drive freely. Some chinese tourist boats offer driving very close to North Korean river bank.

zhDesc: 一个拿着拐杖，抽着烟斗，穿着风衣的男士在江边散步，在游人中十分出格。
enDesc: A gentle man walks along the river bank, with a cane, a smoking pipe, and a coat. He stands out from the tourists crowd.

zhDesc: 婚礼上的“LOVE”，至少都包含了正确的四个字母。
enDesc: “LOVE” of a wedding. At least both contain the correct four characters.

zhTitle: 一列火车从朝鲜开入中国
enTitle: A Train from North Korea to China

enDesc: A train drives from North Korea into China, with its siren on.

zhDesc: 朝鲜的火车头挂着一节车厢。
enDesc: The North Korean train has one locomotive and one compartment.

zhDesc: 鸭绿江边的房子。看起来好像就是我小时候住过的那种，我还依稀记得那个钟楼。
enDesc: The houses by the side of the street along Yalu River. It seems like those kind of houses I stayed in as a child, and I have a little memory of that clock tower.

zhTitle: 刻着“鸭绿江”的塑料石头
enTitle: Plastic Stone Inscribed with Yalu River
zhDesc: 供游人拍照的“石头”，刻着鸭绿江，实际是塑料的。下面有轮子，晚上可以推走。用绳子规定在灯柱上。
enDesc: The “stone” inscribed with “Yalu River” is made in plastic. There are wheels on the bottom so it can be pushed away at night. It’s fixed on the pole by rope.
